sandy-hooker
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a musterer from the Nelson/Marlborough area, whose beat includes shingle and sandy outcrops.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
